ng the examples of\ngastrulation, somitogenesis, and limb skeletal development, I provide instances\nof, and a conceptual framework for understanding, the relationships between\ntransparently physical and evolved types of developmental self-organization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Aug 2021 19:50:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 21:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-24"}
