selectivity. The proposed\ncompensation factor to the joint detector is found to be essential for\nrecovering the transmitted signal in the absence of phase-tracking pilots.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 02:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 06:40:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
