ore and after the\npandemic. These results suggest that pandemic remote learning had very\ndifferent impact for students with different demographic background, and future\ninstructional design should strive to provide more flexible options to meet the\nvarious needs for a diverse higher-ed student population.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 02:20:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-03"}
