LA abundances. We investigate the adoption of a simple,\nobservationally motivated Initial Distribution of Rotational Velocities for\nLC18 and find a slight improvement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 06:40:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2021 00:53:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Dec 2021 19:55:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
