 SR model to facilitate a real-time\nHR prediction in metropolitan areas by combining it with an LR\nbuilding-resolving LES model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 12:22:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 15:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
